https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi

windows install zip file

https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.8.4/binaries/apache-maven-3.8.4-bin.zip

install this maven on 
C:\Program Files (x86)\Maven

Once done 
add 



add path 
#search for control panel --> advnace system setting --> environment variables --> system varialbe --> new 
#Name: MAvEN_HOME 
#Path: C:\Program Files (x86)\Maven\apache-maven-3.8.4


Once add MAVEN_HOME VARIABLE update same path on "Path" variable till /bin
#Path: 
#add : C:\Program Files (x86)\Maven\apache-maven-3.8.4\bin

click on Ok 

open new CMD and check maven version using

mvn 
mvn -version

C:\Users\vinod>mvn -version
